rows.label: qst201507_msg0003
rows.name:
When I was watching, he was holed
up in his room the entire time.

rows.label: qst201507_msg0005
rows.name:
What do we do, mo? Storm
in all at once, mo?

rows.label: qst201507_msg0006
rows.name:
If you want, Hana can launch a
special missile, one big boom-

rows.label: qst201507_msg0007
rows.name:
No, if we do that, everything
will be blown away!

rows.label: qst201507_msg0009
rows.name:
I believe there was a Nopon
helper. I think that person would
know what's going on inside.

rows.label: qst201507_msg0010
rows.name:
Then let's try talking
to that Nopon helper.

rows.label: qst201507_msg0011
rows.name:
She only comes out in the early
morning. Let's catch her then and ask.

rows.label: qst201507_msg0012
rows.name:
Azami really knows a scary
amount of things, mo.

rows.label: qst201507_msg0013
rows.name:
Not at all. I only know
what I've seen while
watching from the shadows...
